cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.SE, cs.RO 

This paper presents an evolutionary algorithm for multi-objective optimization, which is a common topic in the field of computational intelligence and machine learning (cs.NE). The algorithm also incorporates advanced goal and priority specifications, which are typical features of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and control systems (cs.SY). The application of the algorithm to the design optimization of a servo control system for hard disk drives also suggests relevance to software engineering (cs.SE) and robotics (cs.RO).
